    "headline": "Emerson Electric (NYSE:EMR) Misses Q1 CY2026 Sales Expectations",
    "summary": "Engineering and automation solutions company Emerson (NYSE:EMR) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026 as sales rose 2.9% year on year to $4.56 billion. On the other hand, the company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $4.80 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.54 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.",
